<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Welcome to Collegium</title>

  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #1d4ed8;
    }

    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: auto;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #dbeafe, #ffffff, #bfdbfe);
    }

    .header img {
      width: 90px;
      height: auto;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .title {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #1d4ed8;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #1e3a8a;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 18px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      background-color: #1d4ed8;
      color: white !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .footer {
      padding: 15px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #1e40af;
      background: #dbeafe;
    }

    @media(max-width: 480px) {
      .title { font-size: 20px; }
      .content { font-size: 15px; }
      .btn { padding: 10px 16px; }
    }
  </style>

</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
      <img src={{logoUrl}} />
      <div class="title">Welcome to Collegium</div>
      <div class="subtitle" style="color:#1e40af;">
        Create ‚Ä¢ Connect ‚Ä¢ Collaborate
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi <strong>{{fullName}}</strong>,</p>

      <p>
        Thank you for showing interest in <strong>Collegium</strong> ‚Äî the platform
        that empowers students, creators, and communities.
      </p>

      <p>
        Your details:<br/>
        <strong>Email:</strong> {{email}} <br/>
        <strong>University:</strong> {{university}}
      </p>

      <p>
        You will be among the first to experience our upcoming app where you can:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>‚ú® Create your profile and showcase your journey</li>
        <li>ü§ù Connect with students, clubs, and opportunities</li>
        <li>üöÄ Collaborate on projects, events, and communities</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        We will notify you as soon as the app becomes available.  
        Stay ready ‚Äî exciting things are coming!
      </p>

      <p style="margin-top:25px;">
        <strong>Warm Regards,<br/>The Collegium Team</strong>
      </p>

      <a href="https://collegium.asiandigitalworld.com" class="btn">
        Visit Our Website
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
      ¬© Collegium 2025 ¬∑ Create | Connect | Collaborate  
      <br />
      You received this email because you expressed interest in our platform.
      <br/> Automated Email ‚Äî Do Not Reply.
    </div>

  </div>
</body>
</html>